<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Relat√≥rio do Associado</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      padding: 30px;
      padding-top: 0px;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      background-color: #fff;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      color: #4B0082;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .header p {
      color: #555;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin: 5px 0 0;
    }
    .user-card {
      position: relative; /* necess√°rio para o ::before */
      margin-top: 30px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f9f9ff, #f1f3fa);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      overflow: hidden; /* garante que nada vaze fora do radius */
    }

    .user-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 4px; 
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #6C63FF, #4B0082); 
      border-top-left-radius: 12px;
      border-bottom-left-radius: 12px;
    }
    .avatar {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6C63FF, #4B0082);
      color: white;
      border-radius: 50%;
      width: 70px;
      height: 70px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-right: 20px;
    }
    .user-info {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: self-start;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .user-name {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #333;
    }
    .status {
      background-color: #D1FAD7;
      color: #008000;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: bold;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 20px;
    }
    .info-container {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
    .info-box {
      flex: 1;
      background-color: #F9F9FF;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }
    .info-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: #4B0082;
      font-size: 14px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #EEE;
      padding-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .info-item {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .info-item .label {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #555;
    }
    .info-item .value {
      color: #333;
      text-align: right;
    }
    .address-section {
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
    .address-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #4B0082;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .address-box {
      background-color: #F0F8FF;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 18px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .stats-container {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .stat-box {
      flex: 1;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6C63FF, #4B0082);
      color: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 10px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .stat-number {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .stat-label {
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #888;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .fixed-logo {
      height: 120px;
      width: auto;
      z-index: 1;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="header">
    <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="Logo" class="fixed-logo" />
    <h1>Relat√≥rio do Associado</h1>
    <p>Informa√ß√µes Completas e Detalhadas</p>
  </div>

  <div class="user-card">
    <div class="avatar">{{initials}}</div>
    <div class="user-info">
      <span class="user-name">{{name}}</span>
      {{#if isActive}}
        <span class="status">ATIVO</span>
      {{/if}}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="info-container">
  <div class="info-box">
    <div class="info-title">üìã Informa√ß√µes Pessoais</div>
    <div class="info-item"><span class="label">Nome Completo:</span> <span class="value">{{name}}</span></div>
    <div class="info-item"><span class="label">CPF:</span> <span class="value">{{cpf}}</span></div>
    <div class="info-item"><span class="label">Data de Nascimento:</span> <span class="value">{{birthDate}}</span></div>
    <div class="info-item"><span class="label">Email:</span> <span class="value">{{email}}</span></div>
    <div class="info-item"><span class="label">Telefone:</span> <span class="value">{{phone}}</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="info-box">
    <div class="info-title">üèõÔ∏è Informa√ß√µes da Associa√ß√£o</div>
    <div class="info-item"><span class="label">Data de Ades√£o:</span> <span class="value">{{joinDate}}</span></div>
    <div class="info-item"><span class="label">Categoria:</span> <span class="value">{{category}}</span></div>
    <div class="info-item"><span class="label">Status:</span> <span class="value">{{status}}</span></div>
    <div class="info-item"><span class="label">Dependentes:</span> <span class="value">{{dependents}}</span></div>
    <div class="info-item"><span class="label">√öltimo Pagamento:</span> <span class="value">{{lastPayment}}</span></div>
  </div>
  </div>

  <div class="address-section">
    <div class="address-title">üìç Endere√ßo Completo</div>
    <div class="address-box">
      {{address.street}}, {{address.number}}<br>
      {{address.neighborhood}}<br>
      {{address.city}} - {{address.state}}<br>
      CEP: {{address.zip}}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="stats-container">
    <div class="stat-box">
      <div class="stat-number">{{daysAsMember}}</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Dias como Associado</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-box">
      <div class="stat-number">{{dependents}}</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Dependentes</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-box">
      <div class="stat-number">‚úî</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Status Atual</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    Este relat√≥rio foi gerado automaticamente pelo sistema de gest√£o de associados.<br>
    Gerado em: {{generatedAt}}
  </div>

</body>
</html>
